title: Business-Card-Version-135792888473fdc7c5-6004-4c06-8491-56df8c664ea7.png
comments.comment: Not sure how practical it is, but certainly more interesting for those recruiters than be bothered looking. I didn't know about this site, but I was playing around with creative ideas for CVs while job hunting in 2011 and in the end went back to a standard text format in Word - unfortunately, that is all most job advertisements will accept.; truly "monumental" ;-)
